@rhatdan Thanks for pointing that out.  Actually the tests ran clean, the problem seems to be related to uploading the console logs.  If you click through the links, you'll see a message:

```Failed to upload logs: io.grpc.StatusRuntimeException: UNAVAILABLE: io exception```

That's an error w/in the cirrus-system somewhere, nothing we have visibility of.  If it happens a lot, we should contact their support.  For now, I'll just click the 're-run' button.
